history.content:
Seniors had earlier appointments so are likely to be closer to the front of the waitlist, other than that there is no priority for seniors. Only cs/eecs majors will be enrolled until the end of phase 2 and then it will be just waitlist order.

Expansion may happen but I won't know until I am able to make it happen so if it doesn't look like the class got bigger on the schedule I won't be able to provide any guesses.

Can we expect enrollment expansion for upperdivs like 188 and 161?

Also, is the waitlist processed first in first out, or do seniors get priority?
history.subject: Enrollment Expansion for Upperdivs
